      "content": {
        "title": "Forearm Fractures and Monteggia Injuries — Core Principles",
        "definition": "Radius and ulna shaft fractures and Monteggia fracture-dislocations involving ulnar fracture with radial head dislocation.",
        "summary": "Anatomic restoration of forearm rotation is critical. Monteggia injuries require radial head reduction and ulnar fixation to restore stability."
      },
